{"tid":2114405,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果在9月2日公佈，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊。","createTime":"2020-07-18T19:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:14:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c22334491fad28d57904b374da990a936dfab81a","tid":2114405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:36:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/EGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FEGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBz%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=79e56701\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FEGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4%2F&h=e75b14cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/EGO3VUJRIDBCTTUD3WFK34GIZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果在9月2日公佈，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊。</span><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷「爭取休息」：靠選民自主配票<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派初選結束，.................................<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公民黨林瑞華戰飲食界撼張宇人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M5AUL65xsFfgGMtnKQeeArZqTtk=/553x354/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEOSSJMDTY6EJRXPKWKXSGNHU4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM5AUL65xsFfgGMtnKQeeArZqTtk%3D%2F553x354%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEOSSJMDTY6EJRXPKWKXSGNHU4.gif&h=09223266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼區諾軒後，趙家賢亦宣佈退出35+協調工作；圖為民主派初選記者會。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢退出35+協調工作<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢昨發聲明。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n初選發起人戴耀廷於昨晚於facebook發帖，指隨着初選投票完成，各區都產生了出選隊伍，民主派35+初選協調主要工作已完成，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">而到選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果在9月2日，即選前4天公佈，一些區參選團隊會按民調結果停止選舉工程，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊，之後就要靠近二百萬名選民，「由所有人一起來完成這看似是不可能的任務」。</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n戴繼而指，作為民主派35+初選的協調者，到此階段餘下需要做的已不多，未來一段日子會爭取多一些休息時間，也可以更專注於學術的工作，但補充指不是甚麼也不做，「我必會與所有認同民主普選的香港人走在一起，在各自的位置，為達成這目標，繼續努力，直至民主普選臨到香港」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位初選牽頭人、........................................"},{"pid":"73edda0296c560ff3213032c424e4badd7e712a5","tid":2114405,"uid":55854,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"屌，一日做到幾個民調先？個民調係米兩星期做到61萬以上先？唔係嘅話，唔覺得要睇重民調。"},{"pid":"6d57c8bd00a5c93b4b3c085ed13e8364cd5ef574","tid":2114405,"uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MLqEqs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MLqEqs.png&h=d7a97cff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52b2213735c6702688e910371dcf145cd84e78c4","tid":2114405,"uid":82640,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"73edda0296c560ff3213032c424e4badd7e712a5","tid":2114405,"uid":55854,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"屌，一日做到幾個民調先？個民調係米兩星期做到61萬以上先？唔係嘅話，唔覺得要睇重民調。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T01:31:04.000Z","msg":"其實random sample做一千個都準<br />\n大家唔好睇少統計數字嘅強大<br />\n<br />\n但問題係佢地點確保統計人士背景符合實際人數比例<br />\n否則61萬次訪問都無用，只係一個放大咗嘅偏見數據"},{"pid":"8979ce2ae885fecf5c0a297e34a001298814cc9a","tid":2114405,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷：到時候，大家只需聰明地把選票平均分配到各區的民主派候選名單 #社評<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108002</a>"},{"pid":"3d2a755c1052d97f1d49f6acf826e0f1247619d7","tid":2114405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷：到時候，大家只需聰明地把選票平均分配到各區的民主派候選名單 #社評<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108002</a>"},{"pid":"74b13758a83fbf28df64675bb6764ac3d99a6